Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家世也无可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,范乌哲防卫事务交由正规军的巴贝尔少校负责
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必不辜负达蒙将军阁下厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那里原为义勇军监管地区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命熟悉当地的人去方为上策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否有些自我膨胀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算立下过一两次战功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但终究是义勇军 请自重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕罗特上尉 既然求战欲望如此强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如跑一趟巴里亚斯沙漠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴里亚斯沙漠？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那里毫无战略价值可言…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目击情报称在那里发现帝国兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要前往侦查 不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺从就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人顺从是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好兴致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来如何 格雷戈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁 说话好刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 是格雷戈尔 有名的严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁殿下外出未归 真逍遥自在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非趁机 我这人平时就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何时拿下范乌哲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数日内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的性格来说够急的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急欲挽回克罗汀的失利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人说成是无能之辈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼 我只是想说切忌急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经的仇敌给你一句忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每逢季节更替 这块旧伤就会告诫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信黑骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是帝国人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是菲拉尔德人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}菲拉尔德：被帝国吞并的小国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我是否着急 确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手收拾那辆坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还命令人家去送死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上最可怕的就是男人的嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法容忍义勇军第三中队打了一场漂亮仗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 为什么又是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认赌服输 掏钱掏钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高 你好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是第一小队里的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌博行为是被明令禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必呢 一本正经的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来吧 大家都是被晾在一边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅面包房 巴里亚斯分店开张了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有炉子 用铁锅试着烤的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来虽然一般 味道很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅·梅尔姬沃特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是面包师 而是义勇军士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是义勇军士兵 同时也是面包师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳不离手曲不离口嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客气什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心长不高喔 拉玛尔·瓦鲁特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着你管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来找队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我陪你一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉 维尔金在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥没来过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找的是法尔迪奥·兰扎特队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是第七小队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥和维尔金一起失踪的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节维尔金喜欢对什么进行写生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是人所为 不如说是偶发的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从考古学角度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难以赞同你的观点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵览史籍「达鲁库斯之灾」显然是人有意而为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金 法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护窝蜥蜴找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么艾丽西娅会知道护窝蜥蜴？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩同时失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是法尔迪奥陪维尔金去写生了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名侦探也相形见绌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明平日对我们很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 在意的人是他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 拉玛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 大家都是值得信任的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会四处张扬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七小队缺少作为军人的自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了点名 就飘飘然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这话怎么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说队里还有达鲁库斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我听下你们的意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于达鲁库斯之灾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我们还在针对达鲁库斯之灾的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行严肃认真的探讨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 有必要现在谈这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉和艾丽西娅 不感觉好奇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在2000年前 发生在脚下这片土地上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 拉玛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在正站在历史事件的现场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴里亚斯遗迹近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 此行是为完成侦查任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个死板的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是传说神话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说那是瞎编的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有被达鲁库斯人烧毁的城市遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达鲁库斯人焚烧大地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神族人将其击败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是历史上的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这里 法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为所谓的“达鲁库斯人烧毁城市”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是事后人们的主观认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 如果我生活在当时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会无故把自己的财产付之一炬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你的意思是从逻辑上无法解释
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达鲁库斯人自身对灾难传承的缺失也令人不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有众多历史学家对此表示疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉辩论起来相当厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对自己的论点也有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么伊莎拉 归根结底…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你们三个无视我和拉玛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家一起来讨论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听完我们的讨论 有什么想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnite精炼工厂由于人员不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有平日里五成的产量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达鲁库斯人不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 占居民总数的三成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得达鲁库斯人在校生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和14岁以下儿童不用动员入伍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们也干活就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnite是国家之本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须维持生产量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 义勇军完成撤退了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 义勇军只会给正规军添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要说服维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 这些都要带去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 难得来巴里亚斯一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会实地调查的话 再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长变了 是因为他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七小队 那群吊儿郎当不务正业的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么说 或许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意范乌哲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢的战斗为什么要眼睁睁的丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 高官们个个如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非自己吃到苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则不会醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦头…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 你认为能赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是相同意见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴贝尔少校必败
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 拉玛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士也需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本也需要带去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19:00回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会对那种地方感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有考古新发现 必须感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我也得去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左拥右抱 还不满意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有异样声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是汽化器的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你都能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的特长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车程10到15分钟左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看快到了 现在放弃让人不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走也能走过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里等 和汉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来也可以修啊 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉 是因为传说的缘故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非在意这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有人为此感到不快 还是避免为好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是指桑骂槐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等你们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉可固执了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这里就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要有人监视是否有敌人出没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧、好奇心与好感 是如此相似
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 拉玛尔很在意伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且不说维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅怎么也大惊小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是很喜欢法尔迪奥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明这是两种完全不同的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之 艾丽西娅说的“他喜欢法尔迪奥”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于狼对狼群首领的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是为你才留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快修好它！不难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有光线射入也如此明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为石壁中富含Ragnite的结晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 据说这里曾经是采掘场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙上好像刻有记号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是古代Northern（北方）文字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不仅是女武神人的圣地 还是图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图书馆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙上记述的是女武神人与达鲁库斯之灾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不堪回首的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪回首 是对谁而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一切而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人与达鲁库斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对整个世界 都是不堪回首的愚蠢故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贪得无厌者将所有家禽果实据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 并凭借其邪法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将巴里亚斯平原化为焦土
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续读 赛尔贝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大悲 怒而将长矛朝向贪得无厌者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青焰之矛刺穿贪得无厌者的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地从此恢复生机盎然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是达鲁库斯人自己焚毁的城市旧址
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说女武神人建造这座神殿安抚魂灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么女武神人也灭亡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拥有神通广大的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达鲁库斯之灾距今不过2000年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到自然淘汰的话 未免过于短暂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亚公国的大公 兰蒂格瑞丝家族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说继承了女武神人的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人的真相 现在已经成为一个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些碑文全部完成解读的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能解开这个谜？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 包括达鲁库斯之灾的细节在内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有许多事未被提及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊天发现啊 没想到别有洞天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惊人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 你是幸运女神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了全新的碑文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定女武神人之谜也会因此被解开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史又向前迈进一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭…恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会有被更多人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先睹为快不算为过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不知会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我别去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去为好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐等达蒙那样的老狐狸抢走功劳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣的话 你可以先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个目睹 这是件很了不起的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 原来传说的细节在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我上面写着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是伊莎拉她们跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问人姓名前 理应先自报家门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:45.83,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.84,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}思い出は僕を　海辺に導く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:22:00.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心地良さばかりを　求めて生きていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.44,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ぐるぐる同じ場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:25.18,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}そんな僕の前に　現れた笑顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:28.91,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太陽のようだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:37.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:41.48,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:47.14,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}笑い合えるように　唄い合えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:52.25,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:56.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:45.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想见你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飞奔出门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}回忆将我 引向海边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:22:00.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘风飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一味追求安逸的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}原地踏步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:25.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出现在我面前的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:28.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}像太阳般灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:37.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想见你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:41.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飞奔出门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:47.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想和你共同欢笑歌唱
